  ----------
  
  Requirements:
  Apache Ant - http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi
  Java JRE - http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html

  Note: Ant is only required for application building.


  Building the project:
  1/ download and extract all project files to some directory (DIR)
  2/ open the command line, change working directory to DIR
  3/ run the following command: ant compile jar

  Running the project:
  In the same directory as mentioned above, run the following command: ant run
 